creator: Red Bull Apps
descriptionHtml:
With the official FC Red Bull Salzburg App powered by A1 you can receive all the info on the Red Bulls straight on your iPhone!

Latest news, videos, fixtures, live match updates, press conferences and the training schedule for the boys are now on hand for you.

Plus with user-defined push notifications you will be updated with news and developments as they happen.

Should you wish, you can change the language in the settings to read all content in German.


CONTENTS
- LIVE (Ticker incl. live updates, statistics & line-up)
- Real-time PUSH NOTIFICATIONS (Topics: matches, offers, news)
- Latest FC Red Bull Salzburg NEWS
- VIDEOS incl. live streams of our press conferences
- TEAMS (Overview of squads)
- SEASON (Fixtures, table, training schedule)
- CALENDAR (Save all the fixtures in your calendar with an iCal file)
- TICKETS (Match ticket info, online shop)
- RED BULL ARENA (Stadium, arrival, tours)
- SOCIAL MEDIA (All channels at a glance)

The FC Red Bull Salzburg app offers exclusive content for fans and stadium visitors.

In addition to the essential features of a top club app, like live scores, News, the standings and many more, the application includes Augmented Reality-Features as well as innovative functions, like Stadium Vision.

All stadium visitors can enjoy LIVE-Features, which can only be used within the Red Bull Arena. Instant Replay of all important scenes and detailed player statistics make your stadium visit the perfect experience.
